style=\"color:var(--sh-identifier)\">sudo</span><span class=\"sh__token--space\" style=\"color:var(--sh-space)\"> </span><span class=\"sh__token--identifier\" style=\"color:var(--sh-identifier)\">reboot</span><span class=\"sh__token--break\" style=\"color:var(--sh-break)\"></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>After login, I used the following command to update and upgrade the packages that came with the install:</p>\n<pre><code><span class=\"sh__line\"><span class=\"sh__token--identifier\" style=\"color:var(--sh-identifier)\">sudo</span><span class=\"sh__token--space\" style=\"color:var(--sh-space)\"> </span><span class=\"sh__token--identifier\" style=\"color:var(--sh-identifier)\">apt</span><span class=\"sh__token--space\" style=\"color:var(--sh-space)\"> </span><span class=\"sh__token--identifier\" style=\"color:var(--sh-identifier)\">update</span><span class=\"sh__token--space\" style=\"color:var(--sh-space)\"> </span><span class=\"sh__token--sign\" style=\"color:var(--sh-sign)\">&amp;</span><span class=\"sh__token--sign\" style=\"color:var(--sh-sign)\">&amp;</span><span class=\"sh__token--space\" style=\"color:var(--sh-space)\"> </span><span class=\"sh__token--identifier\" style=\"color:var(--sh-identifier)\">sudo</span><span class=\"sh__token--space\" style=\"color:var(--sh-space)\"> </span><span class=\"sh__token--identifier\" style=\"color:var(--sh-identifier)\">apt</span><span class=\"sh__token--space\" style=\"color:var(--sh-space)\"> </span><span class=\"sh__token--identifier\" style=\"color:var(--sh-identifier)\">upgrade</span><span class=\"sh__token--break\" style=\"color:var(--sh-break)\"></span></span></code></pre>\n<h2>Now what?</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Learning Curve</strong>:</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Challenges</strong>:</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Conclusion</h2>\n<h2>Artifacts</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://claude.ai/public/artifacts/af8635e3-14e0-426a-bb4b-c7b11dec1efa\">Claude: Building a Career-Boosting Homelab Development Server</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>References</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/wsl/install\">How to install Linux on Windows with WSL</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://phoenixnap.com/kb/wget-vs-curl\">wget vs curl: What Are the Differences?</a></li>\n</ul>\n<hr/><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"mt-24 border-t border-zinc-100 px-0 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><a href=\"https://github.com/ibelick/nim\" target=\"_blank\"><div class=\"relative inline-block whitespace-nowrap text-xs text-zinc-500\"><div style=\"opacity:1;transform:none\"><span>Â© 2025 Walkable Limited Liability Company</span></div></div></a><div class=\"text-xs text-zinc-400\"></div></div></footer></div></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-6caf1cd8559327c9.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[1362,[\\\"573\\\",\\\"static/chunks/573-02315a3eecce1b14.js\\\",\\\"822\\\",\\\"static/chunks/822-2fbd13d98e76e669.js\\\",\\\"177\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/layout-492b08807980620c.js\\\"],\\\"ThemeProvider\\\"]\\n3:I[6738,[\\\"573\\\",\\\"static/chunks/573-02315a3eecce1b14.js\\\",\\\"822\\\",\\\"static/chunks/822-2fbd13d98e76e669.js\\\",\\\"177\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/layout-492b08807980620c.js\\\"],\\\"Header\\\"]\\n4:I[7555,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n5:I[1295,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n6:I[7716,[\\\"573\\\",\\\"static/chunks/573-02315a3eecce1b14.js\\\",\\\"822\\\",\\\"static/chunks/822-2fbd13d98e76e669.js\\\",\\\"177\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/layout-492b08807980620c.js\\\"],\\\"Footer\\\"]\\n7:I[4970,[],\\\"ClientSegmentRoot\\\"]\\n8:I[691,[\\\"573\\\",\\\"static/chunks/573-02315a3eecce1b14.js\\\",\\\"601\\\",\\\"static/chunks/601-5e7d8c4406619052.js\\\",\\\"998\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/projects/layout-2fd2a2a9ec7e56e1.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n1a:I[8393,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/media/569ce4b8f30dc480-s.p.woff2\\\",\\\"font\\\",